# Assets Loan Security Amount

## identifier
de15163

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of an asset (or assets) pledged by the borrower or a third party against a loan.  In the event of default by the borrower, the lender has recourse to this asset.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.LoanSecurity.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.34
- period=instant
